- List item 1
- List item 2
  - Sub-item 1
  - Sub-item 2
> Blockquote
This is a **bold** and *italic* text.
This is a '''highlighted''' and ``emphasized`` text.
    )";

    std::string html = markdownToHtml(markdown);
    std::cout << html << std::endl;

    return 0;
}
